OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry
OL,6,Fevening with plenty of late evening
OL,7,Fsunshine, but cloudier in the east.
OL,8,FRemaining dry overnight with long
OL,9,Fclear spells in the west but cloudier
OL,10,Fin east.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FA dry day with occasional
OL,13,Fcloud and plenty of long sunny spells.
OL,14,FBecoming very warm by afternoon.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FA
OL,17,Flargely dry and settled few days with
OL,18,Fthe odd spot of rain possible at
OL,19,Ftimes. Cloudy at times but still
OL,20,Fplenty of bright or sunny spells.
OL,21,FStill quite warm.
